<br>
On this eve the tribe's more noted members have gathered at the request of the ogre shaman that leads them, Rukkas Breenga. Rukkas looks around the main feasting table at the various faces and nods. <br>
<br>
&quot;Ruk bring yus heer taday to tell yus bout new enemy to bash.&quot;<br>
<br>
The group rumbles at this news and eyes the ogre shaman closely listening closely to his words.<br>
<br>
&quot;Yus all kno da smel of litey of da woods rite?&quot;<br>
