<br>
&quot;Ya der lotsa dem stikin wood elfys in da oasis huntin stufs&quot; Wretched Heart family leader Rakkas interjects.<br>
<br>
Rukkas nods at his brother's input. The ogre shaman grabs a handful of food and shoves it into his huge mouth. Chewing hungrily he swallows the appetizer and gulps down a large mug of ogre swill and then continues his speech.<br>
<br>
&quot;Well da udder day wen me bring yus to da tokkin hall to speek bout bashin mor liteys so souls can get cupla new slaves fer da fuud servins me got da same stink in me noze as me did in da oasis dat day!&quot;<br>
<br>
The feasting hall roars as trolls, ogres, iksar and dark elves all express their obvious displeasure in this news.<br>
<br>
