<br>
&quot;Aye, your kheros will be ready to dismember any that stand against you&quot; Kishta says, her voice hushed and filled with malice.<br>
<br>
&quot;Meez famly gona slash an splash anyting in da way!&quot; the troll warrior bellows. &quot;Tump famly redy!!&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Ya! So wen we bashin brudder?&quot; ask Rakkas.<br>
<br>
Rukkas grins a wicked toothy grin. &quot;Com. We eet den Ruk tell yus wut me tinkin.&quot;<br>
<br>
Looking around at the broken table and floor soiled with food and drink the ogre shaman shouts down the halls toward the oven room. &quot;Cleen dis mess up an get Ruk new table fer mor eetins nows!!&quot;<br>
