<br>
&quot;RUKKAS!&quot; comes a shout from the entrance of the hall. The ogre shaman turns to see what the commotion is and sees one of the Souls proud members dashing through the halls towards him. Breathing heavily Frakk gives the news of the Emerald Phoenix and their arrival to the forest.<br>
<br>
&quot;HA! dey com fer dey litle frends huh? GUD DEN LETS SEE IF DEY CAN TAKE DEM BAK!!&quot; the ogre roars. <br>
