&quot;Dis wut we gona do. Yus yung Souls go out der an keep dis litle one Frakk got heer safe. Take him wit yus so dem Feenix bashas can see wut we got. Let dem see dat we got him an not letin him go! HEHA! Ruk go find Rak and see wut udder olda souls me can get togedda and we keep da udder hafling wit us. Yus all no fite neer us cuz yus no can do much agenst dem olda seezon fitas. Kill dem yung ones we handle da old. Now GO!&quot;<br>
