<br>
With one of the defenders down more attention could be focused on the shaman which was their next target. Surrounded now the shaman had very little hopes of landing his offensive spells to take down his attackers. The wild dogs bit and kicked at the ogre slowly draining his life from him. Stabbing wildly with his spear Rukkas was intent on damaging the Phoenix members as much as he could to make them pay for their boldness. Very low on health the ogre runs to a safe spot again so that he may heal himself so he can in turn inflict more damage on his attackers. Feeling better the ogre stabs at the wolves again who continue to bite at him and continue to interupt the ice blasts he attempts to land. Again he begins to feel weak as the attacks take their toll on him. Rukkas starts to cast a heal when a wolf bashes him from behind. Spell interupted and short on health the ogre tries again. A blast of energy slams into the ogres large body stunning him. Another blast of energy follows shortly behind knocking the ogre to the ground and rending him unconscious.<br>
